node.accessibility_caption: Photo by INSANE LUXURY in Ponza, Italy with @kingjames, and @rolex. May be an image of 1 person and wrist watch.

node.text:
@kingjames of Lakers during his mediterranean yacht vacation is wearing a new 41mm @rolex Oyster Perpetual ref. 124300 in stainless steel with turquoise ‘Tiffany’ blue dial. Introduced in 2020 the new Oyster Perpetual has been unveiled with a dynamic and vibrant new look, offering lacquer dials in five new colours: candy pink, turquoise blue, yellow, coral red and Rolex green. #Rolex 

Retail price : $5,900.00
Market price : $19,500.00

Photo : @kingjames | @rolex

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by INSANE LUXURY on September 04, 2021 tagging @iamzlatanibrahimovic, and @rolex. May be an image of 1 person and wrist watch.

node.text:
@iamzlatanibrahimovic of AC Milan during the latest Serie A match of his team was wearing a @rolex Daytona ‘Rainbow’ in rose gold, another factory-set Rolex added to his watch collection. This masterpiece is set with 36 baguette-cut rainbow sapphires on bezel, 56 brilliant-cut diamonds on the case and 11 baguette-cut rainbow colored sapphires as hour markers. The Daytona Rainbow was first released in 2012 in 18k white gold and 18k yellow gold, at the time they weren’t much appreciated by the market. #Rolex

Retail price: $ 114,850.00
Market price: $ 425,000.00

Photo : @gettyimages | @rolex

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by INSANE LUXURY in Manhattan, New York with @richardmille. May be an image of 1 person and wrist watch.

node.text:
Jay-Z was recently spotted in NYC wearing his unique @richardmille RM 056 Tourbillon in blue sapphire, especially created for him by the brand. This timepiece is one of the most complicated projects made by RM and it took years of development to be produced. The production of the sapphire case, front bezel, caseband and back bezel is cut and milled from solid blocks of sapphire. The RM056 Tourbillon in blue sapphire has been delivered to Jay-Z in 2019 while the new version (RM056 Tourbillon in green sapphire) in early 2021. #RichardMille

Limited edition: 1 piece
Retail price: $ 2,500,000.00

Photo: @gettyimages | @insaneluxurylife

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by INSANE LUXURY on September 03, 2021 tagging @rohitsharma45, and @geraldcharles_official. May be an image of 1 person and wrist watch.

node.text:
The Indian cricketer and the vice captain of India National team @rohitsharma45 in one of his latest posts was wearing a new @geraldcharles_official Maestro GC 3.0 Chronograph in stainless steel with black dial. The genius of watch design Gerald Genta was inspired by the architecture of Francesco Borromini for the Maestro’s case. The new generation of Maestro timepieces are powered by an ultra-thin movement made by the masters watchmakers of Vaucher Manufacture in Fleurier. #GeraldCharles

Retail price: $ 21,500.00

Photo: @geraldcharles_official

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by INSANE LUXURY on September 03, 2021 tagging @platinumtimesco. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
@platinumtimesco has now available a special @jacobandco Oil Pump Automaton Tourbillon in 18k rose gold, a watch that features a miniature recreation of an oil rig. The pusher at two o'clock starts the two derricks moving, pumping up and down. The dial is a grill evocative of oil rigs, a system of 18k rose gold pipes and wheels connects the various elements above the grill, including an "oil pressure gauge" power reserve and an rose gold oil reservoir. #JacobandCo

Limited edition: 88 pieces
Retail price: $ 380,000.00

Photo: @platinumtimesco

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by INSANE LUXURY in Toronto, Ontario with @champagnepapi, and @patekphilippe. May be an image of 2 people, wrist watch and text that says 'PATEK PHILIPPE 15 1 1 1'.

node.text:
@champagnepapi is about to release his new album ‘Certified Lover Boy’, in this recent shot he was wearing an exclusive @patekphilippe Nautilus 5723/1R-010 in 18k rose gold set with baguette-cut diamonds. This special edition is produced only for Patek’s best customers and not available on the public catalogue. The bezel is set with 32 baguette-cut diamonds and 12 baguette-cut diamonds as hour markers in a chocolate brown dial. #PatekPhilippe

Retail price: $ 143,500.00
Market price: $ 400,000.00

Photo : @champagnepapi | @insaneluxurylife

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by INSANE LUXURY on September 02, 2021 tagging @jacobandco, and @thenotoriousmma. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
Conor Mcgregor’s summer watch hits different! @thenotoriousmma has recently shared pics of his @jacobandco Astronomia ‘Casino’ while chilling by the pool. This special masterpiece is the first grand complication timepiece with a roulette wheel that spins, allowing the owners to play their favorite game of chance at any time. At the press of the button at 8 o’clock position of the case, the roulette wheel is forcefully spun, sending the little white ceramic ball flying. One of the few pieces produced is owned by @champagnepapi. #JacobandCo

Limited edition: 18 pieces
Retail price: $ 620,000.00

Photo: @thenotoriousmma | @jacobandco

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by INSANE LUXURY in London, United Kingdom with @teddysphotos, and @patekphilippe. May be an image of 1 person and wrist watch.

node.text:
Ed Sheeran at tonight’s GQ Men Of The Year Awards 2021 was wearing the new @patekphilippe Nautilus 5711/1300A in stainless steel with green dial and baguette-cut diamonds, one of the most desirable watches by Patek Philippe collectors. This timepiece replaced the iconic blue 5711 in the final year of production of this reference, and this version is additionally set with 32 baguette-cut diamonds on bezel. This version has been introduced in 2021, for the first time a stainless steel Nautilus 5711 has been combined with diamonds. #PatekPhilippe

Retail price : $94,642.00
Market price : $650,000.00

Photo: @gettyimages | @patekphilippe

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by INSANE LUXURY on September 01, 2021 tagging @watchanalytics. May be an image of wrist watch and text that says 'Đ|기 XY CARTIE PARIS CARTIER CRASH AUCTION MARKET ANALYTICS'.

node.text:
Today we are talking about one of the most legendary and mysterious timepieces ever: the Cartier Crash. There are many stories regarding the birth of this watch, some claim it is a tribute to Salvador Dalì's painting 'The Persistence of Memory', while others claim a story according to which the inspiration came thanks to a Cartier Bagnoire who changed the shape of his case following a car accident. This watch made its first appearance in 1967 and even nowadays is one of the most sought after watches on the market. In 1991, the maison created a special edition of 400 pieces for the Paris boutique, as can be seen from the writing on the dial. For this version we have created a graphic that examines the 25 auction results that this watch has achieved in the events of Phillips, Christie's, Sotheby's and Antiquorum. #Cartier

This post has been created in collaboration with @watchanalytics

Photo by INSANE LUXURY in St George's Park National Football Centre with @harrykane, and @patekphilippe. May be an image of 1 person, wrist watch and text.

node.text:
The captain of England National Team @harrykane ahead of the FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 qualification wears a @patekphilippe Aquanaut Chronograph 5968A in stainless steel with orange strap. This timepiece is the first chronograph of the Aquanaut collection and it has been introduced in 2018. It features the classic Aquanaut’s square pattern in dark grey with orange on both the seconds hand and the sub-counter plus other small details. #PatekPhilippe

Retail price: $53,360.00
Market price: $135,000.00

Photo: @england | @patekphilippe

location.name: St George's Park National Football Centre

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by INSANE LUXURY in Los Angeles, California with @kevinhart4real, and @audemarspiguet. May be an image of 1 person, wrist watch and text.

node.text:
@kevinhart4real wears an @audemarspiguet Royal Oak Perpetual Calendar ‘Ultra-Thin’, the world’s thinnest automatic perpetual calendar wristwatch. This watch marks Audemars Piguet’s latest technological milestone with a movement of 2.89mm thick and a case of 6.3mm in height. It features a titanium and platinum case with satin-brushed blue dial and gold applied hour-markers. #AudemarsPiguet

Retail price: $ 162,500.00
Market price: $ 230,000.00

Photo: @kevinhart4real | @audemarspiguet

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by INSANE LUXURY on August 31, 2021 tagging @cristiano, and @rolex. May be an image of 1 person, wrist watch and text.

node.text:
@cristiano arrived at Portugal's football team training session for the upcoming FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 wearing a custom @rolex Cosmograph Daytona 116508 in 18k yellow gold with aftermarket rainbow sapphires bezel. The mother of pearl dial features brilliant-cut diamonds as hour markers and champagne chronograph sub-dials. #Rolex

Photo: @portugal | @insaneluxurylife
